::Hot Rod/Kup::

Kup stands by, looking at his long time friend, as he hears the news.

Hot Rod looks up at Owlhawk.

&quot;Talos is dead, and he wanted me to command. Heh. I failed as a Commander once, I wont do it again. When we get off this planet and return to Cybertron, we will be victorious.&quot;

Kup puts a hand on Hot Rod&#39;s shoulder.

&quot;I think you can handle the pressure of command, Roddy, but dont try to live up to Optimus this time. Be your own bot. Now go inform the troops, Hot... Rodimus.&quot;

Hot Rod smiles.

&quot;I dont have the Matrix, but the Predacon&#39;s will know what it&#39;s like to fight with a real Prime.&quot;

Hot Rod heads for the bridge.

Kup stays behind, and looks at Owlhawk.

&quot;I just hope that when I tell him about Arcee, that he can remain in control.&quot;

